1. INTRODUCTION
TODO: describe the project

2. BUILD
qmake -project
qmake

enter the generated Makefile and replace the following rows:
CC            = gcc
CXX           = g++
with:

CC            = gcc -std=c++0x
CXX           = g++ -std=c++0x

make

3. USAGE
a) run the main server
./main_server
b) run the messenger
./messenger
